Name: Sudoku 9x16x25
About the game: We invite you to plunge into the world of puzzles, prepared for you - Sudoku 9X16X25. The rules are simple - fill in the grid by digits in such a way that they do not repeat horizontally, vertically and in the nearest square. The game have different sizes, difficulty levels and a huge number of puzzles, especially for those who are not afraid of difficult tasks. Under quiet music and pleasant game design, you can brighten up your leisure time and develop your logic skills. The game features: The size of the playing field: 9х9; 16х16; 25х25; Difficulty settings; 150 puzzles for each size (9х9; 16х16; 25х25) User mode User-friendly design Make notes opportunity
